From 788470173f7688c0f427ab4ff41bc7b8d4003a90 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Salis Dev <dev@salis.app>
Date: Thu, 28 May 2026 20:19:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] refactor(packages/ui): rebuild design system for Salis
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Remove GSAP from InputField — packages/ui must be side-effect free
- Replace all hardcoded colors with CSS variables (--salis-*)
- Fix ThemeProvider SSR bug — localStorage only on client
- ThemeToggle now uses Salis tokens
- Button rewritten with CSS variables and inline styles
- InputField uses CSS transitions instead of GSAP
- Add Badge component (default/success/warning/danger/coral)
- Add Card component with optional hover animation
- Update design-tokens.json with full Salis palette
- Update exports in index.ts
- Remove gsap from package.json dependencies
---
